Sentencas: Segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells (SIS-SOFCs) were prepared on flattened-tube partially stabilized zirconia supports.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: The distinguishing characteristic of these cells was the short repeat period, 2.4 mm, and small active cell length, 1.3 min, compared to approximate to 10 mm in previous SISSOFCs.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: The support tubes, formed by gelcasting, were bisque fired and then screen printing was used to sequentially deposit Ni-YSZ anodes, YSZ electrolytes, and Pt-YSZ composite interconnects.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: After high-temperature co-firing, LSM-YSZ and LSM cathode layers were screen printed and fired.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: Each flattened tube side had 12-16 individual cells.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: For testing, the open tube ends were sealed and humidified hydrogen flowed inside of the tubes; air was flowed over the outside of the tubes.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: Maximum total power at 800 degrees C was approximate to 8 W and maximum power density was approximate to 0.7 W cm(-2), calculated using cell active area.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: Good stability was observed during a approximate to 650 h steady-state test.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports

Sentencas: Excellent stability was also observed over 20 redox cycles.
Titulo: Short-period segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells on flattened tube supports
